<li class="nv-edit"><a class="external text" href="../../w/index-title=Template_Campaignbox_American_Civil_War&action=edit.php.html"><span title="Edit this template" style=";background-color: #B0C4DE;;background:none transparent;border:none;">e</span></a></li>
