<ul>
<li>Gugliotta, Guy. <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.nytimes.com/2012/04/03/science/civil-war-toll-up-by-20-percent-in-new-estimate.html?ref=science&pagewanted=all">New Estimate Raises Civil War Death Toll</a>, <a href="The_New_York_Times" title="The New York Times">The New York Times</a>, April 3, 2012, pg. D1 (of the New York edition), and April 2, 2012 on NYTimes.com. Retrieved 2012-04-03 online.</li>
</ul>
